# FinanceMe Banking DevOps Project

An end-to-end DevOps pipeline demonstrating modern CI/CD and infrastructure automation.

## Tools & Technologies Used
- Docker & DockerHub
- Jenkins (CI/CD)
- Ansible (Configuration Automation)
- AWS EC2 (Deployment)
- Prometheus & Grafana (Monitoring)

## Workflow
GitHub → Jenkins → Build Docker → Push to DockerHub → Deploy on AWS via Ansible → Monitor with Grafana

## How to Run
1. Clone the repository.
2. Build Docker image: `docker build -t financeme:latest .`
3. Trigger Jenkins pipeline via `Jenkinsfile`.
4. Provision infrastructure using Ansible and deploy.
5. (Optional) View monitoring dashboard via Grafana.

